  <thing id="spSGAnWhsp" name="Animal Whisper" description="As {i}honeyed tongue{/i} ( Advanced Player’s Guide) but bonus applies only to wild empathy checks you make.\n\n{i}Honeyed Tongue{/i}:\nThis spell augments your diplomacies. While under the effects of spell, you roll two dice each time you make a Diplomacy check to change a creature&apos;s attitude, taking the highest roll. If this results in a roll low enough to reduce the creature&apos;s attitude by a step, that creature gets some clue that you are manipulating it with a spell. Alternatively you can cast this spell before making a Diplomacy check to gather information, gaining a +5 competence bonus on the check." compset="Spell">
